Hadoop Applier Installation:
===========================
1. 1.install and configure hadoop-2.6.0 ($HADOOP_HOME must be set).
2. Download Mysql Source Code from 
 http://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/MySQL-5.6/mysql-5.6.16.tar.gz
3. tar xf mysql-5.6.16.tar.gz
4. cd mysql-5.6.16
5. cmake .
6. make
8. make install

Hadoop-applier:
================
1. Download mysq-hadoop applier
        http://downloads.mysql.com/snapshots/pb/hadoop-applier/mysql-hadoop-applier-0.1.0-alpha.tar.gz
2. tar xvzf mysql-hadoop-applier-0.1.0-alpha.tar.gz
3. cd mysql-hadoop-applier-0.1.0
4. cmake . -DENABLE_DOWNLOADS=1
5. make -j8
6. make install
7. cd /examples/mysql2hdfs/
8. make happlier


