Running hadoop-applier:
=======================

1. WE need to start hadoop first
        >>>> start-all.sh
2. Hive-metastore
       >>>>> hive --service metastore
3. Start Hive 
      >>> hive
4. hive database,table name and columns are must be equal to mysql database,table name..only one change is hiva table conains time_stamp column extra.
5. Start mysql server
        mysql-5.6.16/mysql-test/



